(0) READ-ITEM ARR N
(1) SET I TO 1
(2) IF I GEQ N JUMP TO (10)
(3) SET KEY TO ARR(I)
(4) SET J TO I MINUS 1
(5) IF J LESS 0 JUMP TO (8)
(6) IF ARR(J) LEQT KEY JUMP TO (8)
(7) TRANSFER ARR(J) TO ARR(J+1) DECREASE J BY 1 JUMP TO (5)
(8) TRANSFER KEY TO ARR(J+1)
(9) INCREASE I BY 1 JUMP TO (2)
(10) WRITE-ITEM ARR STOP
